            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Americium sample was bombarded for five weeks",
                "in the Clinton pile. After bombardment the alpha",
                "activity of the sample was observed to consist of",
                "40.3% at 4.1 cm range of 241Am and 59.7% at the 4.7",
                "cm range of 242Cm [formed as a result of the reaction",
                "241Am(n,gamma)242Am(beta-)242Cm]."
              ]
            }
          ],
