          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Cross section was recalculated by NNCSC using 1970s",
                "values for the half lives and branching ratios: 84%",
                "for 16hr Am242 beta branch to Cm242. Assumed Am241",
                "T1/2= 459yr and Cm242 T1/2=163d.",
                "Compiler's comment: The 2018 values for 242Am",
                "T1/2=16.02 h, 241Am T1/2=432.6 y, and 242Cm T1/2=162.8",
                "days. Beta decay branching ratio of 242Am to 242Cm is",
                "82.7%."
              ]
            }
